<p>Dimas, </p>
<p>Its easier than that. </p>
<p><b>WAY</b> easier. </p>
<p>Like one line of code easier. </p>
<p><code>
<pre lang="php" escaped="false">
$metabox-&gt;the_field('description'); 
the_editor($metabox-&gt;get_the_value(), $metabox-&gt;get_the_name());     
</pre>
<p></code></p>
