<div class="comment-text">
<p>Ah ha!!!</p>
<p>Ok I&#8217;ve gotten the Visual/HTML tabs to work. Again, its just a matter of poking around things. </p>
<p><code>
<pre lang="php">
if ( user_can_richedit() )
wp_enqueue_script('editor');
wp_enqueue_script('word-count'); //if you want it
</pre>
<p></code></p>
<p>Now the Style for the text area used by the HTML tab isn&#8217;t quite right but that&#8217;s easy to fix.</p>
</div><!-- .comment-text -->
