<p>Hi &#8211; I am having the same issue as <a href="http://farinspace.com/multiple-wordpress-wysiwyg-visual-editors/#comment-5017" rel="nofollow">Suso above</a> &#8211; line breaks and paragraphs not being retained in the TinyMCE textarea metabox after saving. Has anyone else seen this or been able to fix it? </p>
