<p>Found the issue with the Linebreaks and Paragraph formatting being removed.<br />
The TinyMCE is actually adding those in the field, however it&#8217;s not displaying once you have it on editor side.  Here&#8217;s how to solve it.<br />
Just use wp_richedit_pre(); in your code to echo the content of the text area:</p>
<p> <code></code></p>
<p>So, an example of a custom meta box would be:<br />
