<p>In my metabox template, in the textareas, I am using this:</p>
<p><code>echo wp_richedit_pre($mb-&gt;get_the_value()); </code></p>
<p>In my template for the public page, I am using:</p>
<p><code>echo apply_filters('the_content', $thevariable)</code></p>
<p>This seems to work.</p>
